data.description: Location, Location, Location!! Christmas special ! What a deal!! Seller will contribute to buy down! Can move quickly! The living room features a pretty corner fireplace, luxury vinyl wood look floors, and large windows that let in natural light and showcase the scenic view.  Eat in kitchen with plenty of countertops, and cabinet space. The master bedroom has a walk-in closet, an ensuite bathroom with a garden tub and a separate shower, and his and hers vanities.  The other three bedrooms are also spacious and share a full bathroom . The backyard is serene and relaxing with the view and no neighbors behind you. The home also has a two-car garage, a spacious laundry room, and a formal dining that can be used as an office if needed.  This home is located in an excellent neighborhood, close to John King and I30. This is a rare opportunity to own a beautiful home with a spectacular view. Don’t miss it!
